Package com.verisign.epp.codec.fee.v08 Description

Fee Extension v08 packet encoder and decoder classes (CODEC). The classes in this package can be used to create a fee extension object that can be encoded to XML and decoded from XML. The EPPFeeExtFactory must be registered with the EPPFactory to be able to decode the XML into fee extension objects. The EPPFeeTst class can be used to unit test all of the classes in the package, which includes creating the objects, encoding the XML, decoding the XML, comparing the original object with the decoded object, and finally serializing and de-serializing the object.
